ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T03:48:31.000Z","msg":"去啦 唔去有咩大計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f542a99ed138bd6ede8b05d444be1b17d944177","tid":18934,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:06:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>就算改變唔到，我地都要企出黎！</blockquote><br />\n所以民陣咪呃到咁耐飯食囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n李波 hktv 梁游被 jr 都遊行過喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔遊行咪又係打字，反而遊行後可能有驚喜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n癡線，民陣遊行都咁多人撐。<br />\n督灰割席、龍和道食人血杯麵..... <br />\n<br />\n上次中聯辦大逃亡都唔明，<br />\n人數得咁多，和理非非無裝備，<br />\n黑警大量支援，而且毫不留情。<br />\n仲未計泛民會督灰...... <br />\n<br />\n認真，有事先出去啦。<br />\n打字無用，但唔代表要送死。</blockquote><br />\n依家仲唔叫有事咁點先有事? <br />\n好多大型抗爭活動都係由民陣搞<br />\n咁你係咪就永遠唔參加依類活動?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有事＝突發事件<br />\n<br />\n我真係懷疑你有無出過去。<br />\n講騎劫民陣都講左兩年啦，<br />\n請問有無一次成功過？<br />\n當然無啦，因為泛民有狗賊。<br />\n<br />\n先不論裝備有機會被搜身，<br />\n出到去行一日已經無體力，<br />\n日頭仲要被人點相，<br />\n去民陣遊行都傻傻地。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實集會係好過遊行<br />\n<br />\n有去過遊行都知 每次遊行到尾段 經過幾個樽頸位同黑警閘人之後 D人都會行到好散<br />\n同埋好多人遊行完就走 基本上好難好難召集到人留守等你有咩後續行動<br />\n仲有 由維園行到金鐘添馬艦 有時仲on99行撚到西環 行到去都攰撚到仆街啦 簡直係消耗意志 消耗體力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n集會就唔同<br />\n一來 可以喺同一時間聚集一大班人 又唔洗Set死出發時間 就算有人收工遲成個鐘先join都冇問題<br />\n二來 個個都係準備就緒 體力充足 一有咩爆發點就黎料<br />\n<br />\n你睇雨革魚革都係集會開始而唔係遊行開始就明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bb114fc93e2d94e5023d1db6ceb05f527a5b7ed","tid":18934,"uid":39441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:09:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2396a4658d6c5d47462022616ab16663266177c0","tid":18934,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:14:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除非攪鑊沖擊出黎有人死傷，咁香港人就個個覺得23條係一定要立。依家劇本就係向呢個方向發展。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收撚皮啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家689捂住口笑呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢發覺原來自己咁撚大影響力 乜都唔洗做班人已經嚇到瀨屎<br />\n一時又怕689連任 一時又驚俾位689入 一時又怕689立23條 乜都唔敢做 自己整個框框撚住自己<br />\n不戰而屈人之兵 反對聲音自動收皮<br />\n習總唔俾佢連任鎮住香港都唔得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650fa09c1bda0bdfc9a9023b972bd32406aead8a","tid":18934,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:16:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>除非攪鑊沖擊出黎有人死傷，咁香港人就個個覺得23條係一定要立。依家劇本就係向呢個方向發展。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收撚皮啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家689捂住口笑呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢發覺原來自己咁撚大影響力 乜都唔洗做班人已經嚇到瀨屎<br />\n一時又怕689連任 一時又驚俾位689入 一時又怕689立23條 乜都唔敢做 自己整個框框撚住自己<br />\n不戰而屈人之兵 反對聲音自動收皮<br />\n習總唔俾佢連任鎮住香港都唔得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0850bdda10a6eeeb0323fede5930eaa05d127649","tid":18934,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:22:06.000Z","msg":"等睇鳩做論<br />\n設局論<br />\n連任論<br />\n騎劫論"},{"pid":"df1a7f5bb165ef361eea3d7c4bf9b474ed9a4b8a","tid":18934,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:29:49.000Z","msg":"焦土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9944f39832c32c2d32266878d2bc09c38cd25c9c","tid":18934,"uid":41269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T05:13:35.000Z","msg":"依家啲高登仔討論下都要屌老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce98b087023df0c45c0762a763dd0d8a03303e2","tid":18934,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T05:37:17.000Z","msg":"萬年遊行叫口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪撚消耗民意啦"},{"pid":"127f346b9bdd7f56b3b7613590da4e2c15878bb9","tid":18934,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T05:41:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>萬年遊行叫口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪撚消耗民意啦</blockquote><br />\n而家仲剩幾左？"},{"pid":"a1c4f46a4999c683e2adc35b1574dc63c86f4af5","tid":18934,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T05:46:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好太睇得起自己啦<br />\n如果你因為覺得冇用而唔出去 就算原本有用都會變冇用<br />\n你唔出去唔單單止你唔出去咁簡單<br />\n你會令到其他人都唔想去 <br />\n依個就係強權打壓抗爭既手段<br />\n佢就係希望嚇你班香港人 愈少人 以後就愈易推惡法<br />\n<br />\n點解班五毛 依度時事台都有好幾隻 <br />\n係咁強調出去就要留案底 就係希望香港人唔好出去<br />\n做順民 少d理政治 任何港共玩哂<br />\n<br />\n依個post都有隻啦 扯旗大師</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你睇有幾多人負皮依下先恐怖，依家就算響lihkg都有大量連遊行都屌嘅失敗主意支持者<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a5c4a1defd3d7d1ce0c1aff823f2ca38cf01d4f","tid":18934,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T05:56:44.000Z","msg":"元旦先嚟遊行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65faad9c00b25cc9ef44f2760b9b578f19dc16e0","tid":18934,"uid":35505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T05:56:46.000Z","msg":"遊行一定要出黎<br />\n唔搞法幾十萬人政府只會越踩越過界"},{"pid":"6c192e741a69e120a2ae4fca126120424e6bb2b7","tid":18934,"uid":5801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T06:18:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遊行一定要出黎<br />\n唔搞法幾十萬人政府只會越踩越過界</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除非好似上次咁搞到單雨傘運動，就咁遊行散水既話，以689同土共既無恥性格，我諗就算有一百萬都會扮睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abffe21021755eccc8b7f86024804b211191a03f","tid":18934,"uid":45742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T06:29:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>遊行一定要出黎<br />\n唔搞法幾十萬人政府只會越踩越過界</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除非好似上次咁搞到單雨傘運動，就咁遊行散水既話，以689同土共既無恥性格，我諗就算有一百萬都會扮睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比你攪多次雨傘2.0都冇用啦 政府已經清楚曬香港人個底 你尻坐多七十幾日都冇用"},{"pid":"05deeb0f46b38e84bab751efe76adb47c894a9f0","tid":18934,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T06:30:57.000Z","msg":"比d掌聲自已<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0388bf746d06027aca93ffdd9db98bd805557168","tid":18934,"uid":18648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T06:31:58.000Z","msg":"元旦先搞 on9"},{"pid":"c9478fafb1f2cab64b26466f0ef8334e300ad327","tid":18934,"uid":5801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T06:37:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>遊行一定要出黎<br />\n唔搞法幾十萬人政府只會越踩越過界</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除非好似上次咁搞到單雨傘運動，就咁遊行散水既話，以689同土共既無恥性格，我諗就算有一百萬都會扮睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比你攪多次雨傘2.0都冇用啦 政府已經清楚曬香港人個底 你尻坐多七十幾日都冇用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我意思係好似上次咁搞到單野有號召力，佔馬路緊係係無用，但如果好似太陽花學運咁就唔同玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458712066ed4b1954a0426ad90f5e4b7575fe36c","tid":18934,"uid":2795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T06:42:26.000Z","msg":"叫人唔好去個d我諗本身都無出過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a098361edacbf5fa69d0a80c0063dadbb55be929","tid":18934,"uid":19981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T06:42:42.000Z","msg":"又做show籌錢"},{"pid":"c23bccbd815582e8897aa23df53e4a6047693f8f","tid":18934,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T06:47:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫人唔好去個d我諗本身都無出過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n突破盲點"},{"pid":"d80e1d74e9609318b8c91dea5e656fe9bd5e7864","tid":18934,"uid":11097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T06:51:06.000Z","msg":"又今天我，不了"},{"pid":"50fc55084c961548172d3045de9efe401934a377","tid":18934,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T06:53:17.000Z","msg":"網台做節目屌下咪得囉，你課金班主持就會大大力屌左膠屌遊行班人架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba9912d9c8ae7255ab4ee1b39ad20acbc225d83","tid":18934,"uid":53016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T06:59:08.000Z","msg":"唔join佢都得掛，無其他人搞咩?"},{"pid":"728d04bf73d1bc254259dfd29b09fde097efff92","tid":18934,"uid":8577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:10:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>遊行一定要出黎<br />\n唔搞法幾十萬人政府只會越踩越過界</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除非好似上次咁搞到單雨傘運動，就咁遊行散水既話，以689同土共既無恥性格，我諗就算有一百萬都會扮睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比你攪多次雨傘2.0都冇用啦 政府已經清楚曬香港人個底 你尻坐多七十幾日都冇用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我意思係好似上次咁搞到單野有號召力，佔馬路緊係係無用，但如果好似太陽花學運咁就唔同玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩唔同？<br />\n爆頭方式唔同？"},{"pid":"b295546061a7e56d60ded1cb37cf08a43f2da1f7","tid":18934,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T08:01:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>企出黎又可以改變到d咩？<br />\n不過就算咩都改變唔到<br />\n我都一樣會企出黎<br />\n話比呢個政府聽<br />\n仲有人會反抗<br />\n唔好以為自己大撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出左撐最少係一個表態<br />\n<br />\n下下都要返工，不了，同係屋企做鍵盤戰士，話無功效一樣所以唔做一樣"},{"pid":"0c9d4d1640364644e0463b0160fd2a63ec1e4e4b","tid":18934,"uid":7716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T08:02:59.000Z","msg":"民陣硬係要拖到個議題唔熱再做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5fa6a22b968d0430ad654c2a7df34cd6a5b9b4c","tid":18934,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T08:04:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>叫人唔好去個d我諗本身都無出過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n突破盲點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一語中的<br />\n<br />\n唔好話全部喇，我覺得有唔少人係咁。<br />\n<br />\n老老實實，呢套唔得咪試下第二套<br />\n<br />\n當日咪又係話拆大台，而係馮遊行都話叫唔要大台，咁又有咩搞到出黎？"},{"pid":"5ccad8a4104772dd4b515c6f364561708fa922c8","tid":18934,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T09:14:42.000Z","msg":"理性討論<br />\n係好需要一場大型群眾運動<br />\n睇年初一 中聯辦呢兩次 行動派係嚴重underarmed 比雨革後期旺角甚至金鐘更差 有一大班人佔領咗個據點先更易運到裝備入去 <br />\n當然有和理非多就有可能被人篤灰 但其實係行動派不斷推和理非條底線 由開頭戴頭盔係鬼 到後期成個金鐘都係頭盔 我預計再有佔領 收埋盾都應該冇咩人會篤灰(唔排除有極膠嘅人會啦 自已衡量) 甚至可以令激進泛民幫手量產 將盾變成常規裝備<br />\n同埋最重要係當有一場大型佔領運動 前線可能有啲相對和理非 但上得前線多就會慢慢變成行動派<br />\n但要有群眾就真係要忍手 唔好下下人都唔多就挖磚 唔係唔做 係要有把握先好做 穩守好陣地先好攻 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}